    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This power plant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double-VANOS, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,400 RPM redline. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power through a Variable M Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. This example features the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system, maintaining excellent chassis composure. Mechanically sorted with documented rod bearing and throttle actuator service, it remains a robust performer. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina typical of a well-loved enthusiast car, the structural and mechanical integrity remains sharp and communicative.",
